OL,4,C'in plain view of leaders', report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FA "shocking" level of chaos at scandal-
OL,8,Fhit HMP Wandsworth was the result of
OL,9,Fsustained decline that happened "in
OL,10,Fplain view of leaders", a report by
OL,11,Fthe prisons watchdog has concluded.
OL,13,FPrison staff displayed an "inability
OL,14,Fto account for prisoners during the
OL,15,Fworking day", despite an investment of
OL,16,Falmost #900,000 since Daniel Khalife's
OL,17,Falleged escape in September 2023, a
OL,18,Freport by HM Inspectorate of Prisons
OL,19,F(HMIP) found.
