OL,3,C'Shocking' chaos at HMP Wandsworth was
OL,4,C'in plain view of leaders', report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FThe inspection, which took place from
OL,8,FApril 22 to May 2, found that the
OL,9,Fprison was "severely overcrowded" with
OL,10,F80% of men sharing cells designed to
OL,11,Fhold one person.
OL,13,FAt the time of the inspection, the
OL,14,Fprison held 1,521 men, despite HMP
OL,15,FWandsworth having a baseline
OL,16,Foperational capacity of 979 men.
OL,18,FAround three quarters of men reported
OL,19,Fspending more than 22 hours a day in
OL,20,F"appalling conditions" in their cells,
OL,21,Fthe report noted.
