OL,3,C'Shocking' chaos at HMP Wandsworth was
OL,4,C'in plain view of leaders', report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FInspectors carrying out two random
OL,8,Froll checks were unable to verify this
OL,9,Fbecause "record keeping was so poor",
OL,10,Fwith staff unable to account for where
OL,11,Fprisoners on their wings were.
OL,13,FThe report also found that more than
OL,14,Fhalf of men said it was easy to get
OL,15,Fdrugs and the smell of cannabis was
OL,16,F"ubiquitous".
OL,18,FIt concluded that "inexperience across
OL,19,Fevery grade of operational staff" was
OL,20,Fpreventing them from "bringing about
OL,21,Fmuch needed change".
