OL,3,C'Shocking' chaos at HMP Wandsworth was
OL,4,C'in plain view of leaders', report
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FHM Chief Inspector of Prisons Charlie
OL,8,FTaylor said: "The level of chaos we
OL,9,Ffound at Wandsworth was deeply
OL,10,Fshocking.
OL,12,F"The prison population crisis has
OL,13,Fundoubtedly compounded the pressures
OL,14,Fon the jail, but the appalling
OL,15,Fconditions at Wandsworth did not
OL,16,Fappear overnight and are the result of
OL,17,Fsustained decline permitted to happen
OL,18,Fin plain view of leaders in the jail,
OL,19,FHM Prison & Probation Service (HMPPS)
OL,20,Fand the MoJ whose own systems clearly
OL,21,Fidentified the prison as struggling."
